{"TopicId":123293,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Where\u0026#039;s the EVA headlamp switch?","CreatedByName":"JackBush","CreatedById":149535,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T14:44:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JackBush","CreatedById":149535,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T14:44:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs there a light on the Kerbal\u0027s helmet? If so how do you switch it on when she does an EVA? \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI looked through the Wiki for this but came up empty.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-10-18T14:51:30Z\u0022 title=\u002210/18/2015 02:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 18, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by JackBush\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fuzzy Dunlop","CreatedById":27329,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T14:49:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes there is! press \u0022L\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JackBush","CreatedById":149535,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T14:50:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGreat! Thanks Fuzzy.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yasmy","CreatedById":79995,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T15:43:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFor future reference, look at the EVA section of \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_bindings\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKey_bindings\u003C/a\u003E in the wiki, or from the KSP main menu, select Settings, then Input to see and modify your key bindings.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-10-18T15:49:11Z\u0022 title=\u002210/18/2015 03:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 18, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Yasmy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FlyingPete","CreatedById":127384,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T16:10:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI always set the EVA controls to the same keys as the RCS controls, and control the Kerbal as if he were a ship.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-18T17:31:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve always wondered why they picked a different default hotkey for EVA lights than for ship lights. Seems kinda silly.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}